<p>
    In the previous pod, we learned the formula for work.
    In this pod, we will its companion, the formula for power.
    In fact, there are three formulas for power!
    (Hence the name of this pod: Power Formula<strong>s</strong>.
    The first one is the main one we will use in this unit.
    The second one is also extremely useful,
    and the third one is used in learning electric circuits.
</p>


<h5>
    Formula 1:
</h5>

<p class = 'equation'>
    $$
    P = \frac{W}{\Delta t}
    $$
</p>
